### Test Phase 2 APIs - Product Catalog System

### 1. Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3001/categories

### 2. Get category hierarchy
GET http://localhost:3001/categories/hierarchy

### 3. Get category by slug
GET http://localhost:3001/categories/slug/kitchen-dining

### 4. Get all products
GET http://localhost:3001/products

### 5. Get featured products
GET http://localhost:3001/products/featured

### 6. Search products
GET http://localhost:3001/products/search?q=kitchen

### 7. Get products by category
GET http://localhost:3001/products?category=kitchen-dining

### 8. Get products with pagination
GET http://localhost:3001/products?page=1&limit=10

### 9. Create a new category (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3001/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Test Category",
  "slug": "test-category",
  "description": "A test category",
  "isActive": true,
  "sortOrder": 100
}

### 10. Create a new product (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3001/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "slug": "test-product",
  "description": "A test product for Phase 2",
  "shortDescription": "Test product",
  "sku": "TEST-001",
  "price": 1500.00,
  "comparePrice": 2000.00,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "isActive": true,
  "isFeatured": true,
  "seoTitle": "Test Product - Household Planet Kenya",
  "seoDescription": "High quality test product available at Household Planet Kenya",
  "tags": "test,product,household",
  "images": "[]"
}

### 11. Update product (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "price": 1400.00,
  "isFeatured": false
}

### 12. Bulk update products (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/products/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "productIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "updates": {
    "isActive": true,
    "isFeatured": false
  }
}

### 13. Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/products/1

### 14. Get product by slug
GET http://localhost:3001/products/slug/test-product